    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Melanorivulus ofaie, new species, MCP 50022, paratypes, living females, Rio Verde drainage, upper Rio Paraná basin, Mato Grosso do Sul State, Brazil, Brazil. Photos by Matheus V. Volcan." ;
